room_title: Escape room "Tourist Trap" by Cryptex Escape Rooms in Branson
review: My husband and I did Tourist Trap and had a blast! This was our first escape room experience and we definitely weren't disappointed.

room_title: Escape room "Tourist Trap" by Cryptex Escape Rooms in Branson
review: First time doing an escape room and it was a blast. We did the Tourist Trap and barely escaped with 1 minute to spare. I'd definitely recommend Cryptex!

room_title: Escape room "Tourist Trap" by Cryptex Escape Rooms in Branson
review: We had a great time! Challenging but not so difficult that you can't make any progress. We did Tourist Trap and escaped with just under 2 minutes left on the clock. The staff was great as well.
